msgid "Speed Talisman"
msgstr "Speed Talisman"

msgid "Equipping this talisman increases weapon attack speed and shortens attack recovery. The bonus grows with active Boss Cells."
msgstr "Equipping this talisman increases weapon attack speed and shortens attack recovery. The bonus grows with active Boss Cells."

msgid "A little charm humming with impatient power. The more hostile the island becomes, the faster it urges your hands to move."
msgstr "A little charm humming with impatient power. The more hostile the island becomes, the faster it urges your hands to move."
